But stop telling me lies.

1191
01:24:35.540 --> 01:24:39.860
Stop with hiding some secrets. Okay?

1192
01:24:40.780 --> 01:24:43.140
-I understand.
-Okay.

1193
01:24:44.580 --> 01:24:46.780
